    },
    "As your personal AI health assistant, Hime understands your real-time health data, feels your heart beats, your breath, and your body's movements, and provides proactive insights so you never miss what matters. \n\nFully self-hosted, fully local, secure, and open-source. Say **Hi** to healthy **Me**!" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "As your personal AI health assistant, HiMe understands your real-time health data, feels your heart beats, your breath, and your body's movements, and provides proactive insights so you never miss what matters. \n\nFully self-hosted, secure, and open-source. Say **Hi** to healthy **Me**!"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作为您的个人AI健康智能体，HiMe理解你的每一次心跳，每一次呼吸，每一次运动，并且主动提供健康洞察，从不错过。\n\n完全由您自己搭建服务器，安全，开源。Say **Hi** to healthy **Me**!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "As your personal AI health assistant, Hime understands your real-time health data, feels your heart beats, your breath, and your body's movements, and provides proactive insights so you never miss what matters. \n\nFully self-hosted, secure, and open-source. Say **Hi** to healthy **Me**!" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "作为您的个人AI健康智能体，HiMe理解你的每一次心跳，每一次呼吸，每一次运动，并且主动提供健康洞察，从不错过。\n\n完全由您自己搭建服务器，安全，开源。Say **Hi** to healthy **Me**!"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Ask your agent to create a personalised page\nand it will appear right here." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ask your agent to create a personalised page\nand it will appear right here."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "让您的智能体创建一个个性化页面,\n它就会出现在这里。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Auth Token" : {
      "shouldTranslate" : false
    },
    "Authorization" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Authorization"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "授权"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Before any data is shared with a third-party AI service, the app requires your explicit consent on the \"AI Data Sharing\" onboarding page. You can withdraw consent at any time in Settings → Data & Privacy → Revoke Consent. Revoking consent disconnects the app from your server and returns you to onboarding; no data is sent until you re-consent. You can also revoke HealthKit access in the iOS Settings app at any time." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Before any data is shared with a third-party AI service, the app requires your explicit consent on the \"AI Data Sharing\" onboarding page. You can withdraw consent at any time in Settings → Data & Privacy → Revoke Consent. Revoking consent disconnects the app from your server and returns you to onboarding; no data is sent until you re-consent. You can also revoke HealthKit access in the iOS Settings app at any time."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "在任何数据被共享给第三方 AI 服务之前，应用会在「AI 数据共享」引导页要求你明确同意。你可以随时在「设置 → 数据与隐私 → 撤回同意」中撤回授权。撤回后，应用会断开与服务器的连接并返回引导流程，在你再次同意前不会发送任何数据。你也可以随时在 iOS 系统设置中撤销 HealthKit 访问权限。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
