    },
    "Collected data is forwarded to the Hime backend server that you deploy and configure in the app's Settings. Your server stores the data locally and uses it to: (a) compute statistics for the on-device dashboard; (b) generate AI-driven health reports and chat replies; (c) trigger health alerts based on rules you define. The app developer never receives any of your data." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Collected data is forwarded to the HiMe backend server that you deploy and configure in the app's Settings. Your server stores the data locally and uses it to: (a) compute statistics for the on-device dashboard; (b) generate AI-driven health reports and chat replies; (c) trigger health alerts based on rules you define. The app developer never receives any of your data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "收集到的数据会转发至你在应用设置中配置的 HiMe 后端服务器。你的服务器将数据存储在本地，并用于：(a) 计算本机仪表盘的统计信息；(b) 生成 AI 健康报告与聊天回复；(c) 依据你定义的规则触发健康提醒。应用开发者永远不会接收你的任何数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Communication between the app and your server uses HTTPS when you configure an HTTPS server URL. An optional bearer token (API_AUTH_TOKEN) authenticates every request when set. Server-side, dynamically generated personalised pages run under a strict Content Security Policy and a sandbox that blocks dangerous imports. SQL accepted from the agent is validated to prevent destructive statements against health data." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Communication between the app and your server uses HTTPS when you configure an HTTPS server URL. An optional bearer token (API_AUTH_TOKEN) authenticates every request when set. Server-side, dynamically generated personalised pages run under a strict Content Security Policy and a sandbox that blocks dangerous imports. SQL accepted from the agent is validated to prevent destructive statements against health data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "当你配置 HTTPS 服务器地址时，应用与服务器之间通过 HTTPS 通信。设置可选的 Bearer 令牌（API_AUTH_TOKEN）后，每次请求都会进行鉴权。在服务器端，动态生成的个性化页面运行在严格的内容安全策略（CSP）与屏蔽危险导入的沙箱中。智能体提交的 SQL 会经过校验，以防止对健康数据执行破坏性语句。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
