    "Data & Privacy" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "数据和隐私"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Data is stored on your iPhone (HealthKit-derived caches, conversation history, configuration in UserDefaults) and on the Hime server you operate (per-user SQLite databases, agent memory, generated reports). Retention is fully under your control: deleting the app removes all on-device data; resetting your server wipes all server-side data. Third-party AI providers may retain prompt/response logs according to their own policies." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Data is stored on your iPhone (HealthKit-derived caches, conversation history, configuration in UserDefaults) and on the HiMe server you operate (per-user SQLite databases, agent memory, generated reports). Retention is fully under your control: deleting the app removes all on-device data; resetting your server wipes all server-side data. Third-party AI providers may retain prompt/response logs according to their own policies."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "数据存储在你的 iPhone 上（HealthKit 衍生缓存、对话历史、存于 UserDefaults 的配置），以及你运营的 HiMe 服务器上（按用户划分的 SQLite 数据库、智能体记忆、生成的报告）。留存期限完全由你控制：删除应用即可清除所有本机数据；重置服务器即可清除所有服务器端数据。第三方 AI 提供商可能会按其自身政策留存提示词/响应日志。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Data travels from this app to the Hime server you deploy, and your server makes API calls to the AI provider you selected. Hime does not upload your data to any service operated by the app developer." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "数据将由app传输到您自己部署的HiMe服务器，您的服务器会通过API调用您自己选择和配置的AI服务。HiMe本身不上传任何数据到其他任何开发者运营的服务上。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
