    "Hime" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime (Health Intelligence Management Engine) is an open-source, self-hosted AI health assistant. The iOS app is a client that communicates only to a backend server that you, the user, deploy and operate yourself. The app developer does not run any server, does not collect telemetry, and does not have access to your data." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe (Health Intelligence Management Engine) is an open-source, self-hosted AI health assistant. The iOS app is a client that communicates only to a backend server that you, the user, deploy and operate yourself. The app developer does not run any server, does not collect telemetry, and does not have access to your data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe（Health Intelligence Management Engine）是一款开源、自托管的 AI 健康助手。本 iOS 应用只与你自己部署并运行的后端服务器通信。应用开发者不运营任何服务器，不收集遥测数据，也无法访问你的任何数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime Home" : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe Home"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe 主页"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime is not directed to children under 13. Do not use the app if you are under the minimum age of digital consent in your jurisdiction." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe is not directed to children under 13. Do not use the app if you are under the minimum age of digital consent in your jurisdiction."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe 不面向 13 岁以下的儿童。如果你未达到所在司法辖区的数字同意最低年龄，请勿使用本应用。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime is ready to go. You can change any of these settings later from the gear icon on the home screen." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe is ready to go. You can change any of these settings later from the gear icon on the home screen."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe 已准备就绪。您可以随时在主界面右上角的齿轮图标中修改这些设置。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime is ready. \n Long press the HiMeow in the home tab and the AI agent will start analysing health trends and pushing reports automatically." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe is ready. \n Long press the HiMeow in the home tab and the AI agent will start analysing health trends and pushing reports automatically."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe准备就绪！\n在主页长按您的HiMeow来唤醒智能体进行一次快速健康分析，并且自动推送健康分析报告"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime is self-hosted, but your server forwards your data to a third-party AI service that you choose and configure. Please review the details below before continuing." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe是您自己搭建的服务，但是您自己搭建的服务器会按照您的选择和配置将数据传送到第三方AI服务。请在继续之前仔细阅读下面的细节。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime monitors 50+ health metrics from your Apple Watch in the background using HealthKit observer queries." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe monitors 50+ health metrics from your Apple Watch in the background using HealthKit observer queries."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe 在后台通过 HealthKit 观察查询持续监测来自您的 Apple Watch 的 50+ 项健康指标。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime Privacy Policy" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe隐私政策"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime reads heart rate, HRV, blood oxygen, sleep, steps, workouts and related metrics from Apple Health so its agent can analyse trends. Hime never writes to Health and never uploads raw samples to third parties." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe reads heart rate, HRV, blood oxygen, sleep, steps, workouts and related metrics from Apple Health so its agent can analyse trends. HiMe never writes to Health and never uploads raw samples to third parties."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe 从 Apple 健康读取心率、心率变异性、血氧、睡眠、步数、锻炼等指标以供智能体分析趋势。HiMe 永远不会写入健康数据,也不会将原始样本上传给任何第三方。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime reads wearable health data from Apple Health so the AI agent can analyse trends. Hime never writes to Health and you have the full control on how and where AI process the data." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe reads wearable health data from Apple Health so the AI agent can analyse trends. HiMe never writes to Health and you have the full control on how and where AI process the data."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe从Apple Health读取可穿戴健康数据，提供给智能体分析健康趋势。HiMe从来不写入更改健康数据，由你自己完全控制在AI在哪里、如何处理你的健康数据。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime requires a self-hosted server. Follow the setup guide on GitHub to deploy your backend and connect this app." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe requires a self-hosted server. Follow the setup guide on GitHub to deploy your backend and connect this app."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe需要您自己搭建服务器。请按照Github上的指南来部署您的服务器并且连接到该app。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime runs on your own server. Follow the Hime GitHub Repo to deploy your own server." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe在您自己的服务器上运行。关注HiMe Github仓库来部署服务器。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Hime sends Apple Health data and chat messages to the third-party AI provider configured on your server. Your explicit consent is required before any data is shared." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe基于您自己搭建的服务器的配置项，将Apple Health数据和智能体聊天记录发送到第三方AI供应商。在任何数据发送之前我们需要您的显式许可。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "HiMeow is a AI digital health avatar that lives on your home screen and reflects your real-time health state. It's happy when you are well-rested, concerned when something looks off. \nLong-press HiMeow anytime for an instant health report and quick AI analysis." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMeow 是您的AI数字健康化身，它会驻留在您的HiMe App主屏幕上，实时反映您的健康状况。当您休息充足时，它会感到高兴；当您的身体出现异常时，它会表示担忧。\n\n随时长按 HiMeow，即可查看即时健康报告和快速的 AI 分析。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How Hime shares your data with third-party AI" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "HiMe如何和第三方AI供应商分享您的数据"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "How it is sent" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "数据如何被发送"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I Agree & Continue" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "我同意&继续"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I understand and agree to share my data with the third-party AI service configured on my server." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "我理解并且同意将数据分享给我服务器上配置的第三方AI供应商"
          }
        }
