    },
    "Your AI digital health avatar" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的AI数字健康化身"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your AI health companion. Hime uses an autonomous on-device agent to analyse Apple Watch data and surface insights you would otherwise miss." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your AI health companion. HiMe uses an autonomous on-device agent to analyse Apple Watch data and surface insights you would otherwise miss."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的 AI 健康伙伴。HiMe 使用设备端自主智能体分析 Apple Watch 数据,挖掘你可能错过的健康洞察。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your control" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "您的控制"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your Hime cat reflects your current health state. Its expression and mood are driven by the agent in real time — happy when you are rested, concerned when something looks off." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your HiMe cat reflects your current health state. Its expression and mood are driven by the agent in real time — happy when you are rested, concerned when something looks off."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的 Himeow会实时反映你当前的健康状态。它的表情和情绪由智能体实时驱动 — 当你休息充分时它会开心,当有异常时它会担忧。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your Hime server makes API calls to a third-party Large Language Model (LLM) provider that you select via the DEFAULT_LLM_PROVIDER setting on your server. Supported providers include: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google (Gemini / Vertex AI), Mistral, Groq, DeepSeek, xAI, OpenRouter, Perplexity, Amazon Bedrock, Azure OpenAI, ZhipuAI, MiniMax, or a self-hosted vLLM endpoint.\n\nWhen the AI agent runs, the following may be sent to the chosen provider: numeric health metrics (with timestamps and units), summaries derived from your data, the text of your messages, and prompts/instructions assembled by the agent. Each provider processes the data under its own terms of service and privacy policy. You can review the providers' policies on their respective websites. We require you to confirm that the provider you choose offers data protection equal to or stronger than what is described in this policy.\n\nHime does not share data with any other third party (no analytics SDKs, no advertising networks, no crash-reporting services that exfiltrate data)." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Your HiMe server makes API calls to a third-party Large Language Model (LLM) provider that you select via the DEFAULT_LLM_PROVIDER setting on your server. Supported providers include: OpenAI, Anthropic, Google (Gemini / Vertex AI), Mistral, Groq, DeepSeek, xAI, OpenRouter, Perplexity, Amazon Bedrock, Azure OpenAI, ZhipuAI, MiniMax, or a self-hosted vLLM endpoint.\n\nWhen the AI agent runs, the following may be sent to the chosen provider: numeric health metrics (with timestamps and units), summaries derived from your data, the text of your messages, and prompts/instructions assembled by the agent. Each provider processes the data under its own terms of service and privacy policy. You can review the providers' policies on their respective websites. We require you to confirm that the provider you choose offers data protection equal to or stronger than what is described in this policy.\n\nHiMe does not share data with any other third party (no analytics SDKs, no advertising networks, no crash-reporting services that exfiltrate data)."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "你的 HiMe 服务器会根据你在服务器上通过 DEFAULT_LLM_PROVIDER 配置的选项，调用第三方大语言模型（LLM）提供商的 API。支持的提供商包括：OpenAI、Anthropic、Google（Gemini / Vertex AI）、Mistral、Groq、DeepSeek、xAI、OpenRouter、Perplexity、Amazon Bedrock、Azure OpenAI、智谱 AI（ZhipuAI）、MiniMax，或自托管的 vLLM 终端。\n\n当 AI 智能体运行时，可能会向所选提供商发送：带时间戳与单位的数值健康指标、基于你数据生成的摘要、你的消息文本、以及智能体构造的提示词/指令。每个提供商会依据其自身的服务条款与隐私政策处理数据，你可在各提供商官网查阅其政策。我们要求你确认所选提供商提供的数据保护不低于本政策所述标准。\n\nHiMe 不与任何其他第三方共享数据（不使用分析 SDK、不使用广告网络、不使用会外传数据的崩溃上报服务）。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
